**Welcome to Gene‚Äôs - Restaurant By The Riverside: A Culinary Gem in Goa Velha**

Nestled along the scenic banks of the river, Gene‚Äôs - Restaurant By The Riverside has gained a devoted following, recently achieving an impressive 4.2 rating from over 2,121 customer reviews. This lively eatery encompasses all that visitors love and expect from a true Goan dining experience. The restaurant is repeatedly highlighted for its stunning views and signature offerings, with tags such as *cheese garlic naan* (36 mentions) and *prawns* (17 mentions) showcasing its culinary highlights.

**Ambiance & Design**

Upon entering Gene‚Äôs, guests are greeted by a cozy yet vibrant atmosphere that perfectly encapsulates the Goan essence. The decor artfully combines local charm with modern comforts, featuring both cozy indoor seating and a picturesque outdoor patio. Patrons can relish their meals while soaking in breathtaking views of the river and Divar Island, set against a backdrop of gentle waves and tropical flora. The warm lighting creates a welcoming ambiance, while the curated music playlist enhances the overall dining experience, making it perfect for both casual lunches and romantic dinners.

![Outdoor Dining](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmjjoq8n0GVFbPUUHE8D044uuatuEozfE5RuZBRMdAQCB_K9cB549Fm_4cljmodUjuw8m65MLBOjprffnmc_hB2zIzkQD3y2R2RVNS1HE_98gDCjVdT9815DKlL8xAdahojWWUd=w375-h281-p)

The menu at Gene‚Äôs is a celebration of flavors, with an emphasis on local Goan cuisine. Signature dishes include the *raw fried prawns*, renowned for their crispy exterior and savory richness, and the *squid masala*, which is beautifully tender and bursting with spice. Patrons have also raved about the *prawn rice*, which is deemed a must-try delicacy that balances textures and flavors perfectly. Not to forget, the *cheese garlic naan* receives high praise for its indulgent taste, cleverly complementing various dishes. Additionally, the menu caters to various dietary preferences, ensuring everyone finds something delightful to enjoy.

![Delicious Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkLvFCs_qWm8MSgoShj93bXP6ec1TUN5Z_TwMFdVBNqI54M5QAGFnB2_-jRaD1ZKDO-sBQIOSENgNt6bJU3u0bkrPL8pqSUAf8qLU4eC37r7BJbmHsfLjmUCl6wD6qdrPu39IR6=w750-h563-p)

The team exhibits a genuine regard for patrons, effectively managing orders and ensuring that dining experiences are seamless. Reservations and walk-in options are available, with reviewers noting that, regardless of visiting hour, the service remains consistently attentive and courteous.

![Friendly Service](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnULhCQSsyxbvCAXtI2jhbSQa7FbWgFKIeRLnJLZZjrBFmE08oSt7t-fz4xPf-2or4BgSjwpYAhoCNthAK46ceIZR1KuHbLXV7jNDtateFJmmWzK045Aa3LiNBVVxiNhKEEaL7_=w375-h281-p)

**Popularity & Reviews**

Gene‚Äôs has established itself as a beloved dining spot in Goa, generating considerable buzz on social media and review platforms. Patrons have taken to sharing their experiences across platforms, encouraging friends and fellow travelers to include Gene‚Äôs in their itinerary. The combination of casual elegance and top-notch cuisine ensures that the restaurant stands out as a must-visit destination for both tourists and locals alike.
